[32mall[32m n[32m:[32mNode[32m {
[32m//[32m There[32m are[32m no[32m directed[32m cycles[32m,[32m i[32m.e[32m.,[32m a[32m node[32m is[32m not[32m reachable[32m
[32m//[32m from[32m itself[32m along[32m one[32m or[32m more[32m travers[32mals[32m of[32m left[32m or[32m right[32m.
[32mn[32m not[32m in[32m n[32m.[32m^([32mleft[32m +[32m right[32m)

[32m//[32m A[32m node[32m cannot[32m have[32m more[32m than[32m one[32m parent[32m
[32ml[32mone[32m n[32m.[32m~[32m([32mleft[32m +[32m right[32m)

[32m//[32m A[32m node[32m cannot[32m have[32m another[32m node[32m as[32m both[32m its[32m left[32m child[32m
[32m//[32m and[32m right[32m child[32m.
[32mno[32m n[32m.left[32m &[32m n[32m.right[32m
[32m}
[32m}

[32mpred[32m Sorted[32m()[32m {
[32mall[32m n[32m:[32mNode[32m {
[32m//[32m All[32m elements[32m in[32m the[32m n[32m's[32m left[32m subtree[32m are[32m smaller[32m than[32m the[32m n[32m's[32m elem[32m.
